text: Kinelle () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Kilinchinsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 96 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Astrakhan, 11 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Kinelle
